Sentencas: Perovskite type complex oxide L0.8Sr0.2CoO3-delta symmetrical cells were prepared on Samaria doped ceria electrolyte Ce0.85Sm0.15O2-x by using the screen-printing method in a laboratory scale.
Titulo: Investigation of La0.8Sr0.2CoO3/Ce0.85Sm0.15O2-x cathode performance of solid oxide fuel cell by electrochemical impedance spectroscopy:: Effect of firing temperature

Sentencas: The performance of the symmetrical cell was investigated by using electrochemical spectroscopy at frequency ranging from 0.1-300 kHz.
Titulo: Investigation of La0.8Sr0.2CoO3/Ce0.85Sm0.15O2-x cathode performance of solid oxide fuel cell by electrochemical impedance spectroscopy:: Effect of firing temperature

Sentencas: Effect of firing temperature from 975-1,050 degrees C was investigated under the controlled oxygen pressure from 0.002-0.21 atm and controlled measuring temperature from 635-782 degrees C.
Titulo: Investigation of La0.8Sr0.2CoO3/Ce0.85Sm0.15O2-x cathode performance of solid oxide fuel cell by electrochemical impedance spectroscopy:: Effect of firing temperature

Sentencas: The preliminary results indicated that, for all cells prepared at different firing temperatures, the SEM and XRD did not indicate any differences between diem.
Titulo: Investigation of La0.8Sr0.2CoO3/Ce0.85Sm0.15O2-x cathode performance of solid oxide fuel cell by electrochemical impedance spectroscopy:: Effect of firing temperature

Sentencas: By using EIS, however, two impedance arcs were obviously observed.
Titulo: Investigation of La0.8Sr0.2CoO3/Ce0.85Sm0.15O2-x cathode performance of solid oxide fuel cell by electrochemical impedance spectroscopy:: Effect of firing temperature

Sentencas: This first arc was found at high frequency region (> 1,000 Hz) and the second one was observed at low frequency region (< 10 Hz).
Titulo: Investigation of La0.8Sr0.2CoO3/Ce0.85Sm0.15O2-x cathode performance of solid oxide fuel cell by electrochemical impedance spectroscopy:: Effect of firing temperature

Sentencas: The high frequency arc corresponded to the impedance of electron-transfer and ion-transfer processes occurring at the current collector/electrode and electrode/electrolyte interfaces.
Titulo: Investigation of La0.8Sr0.2CoO3/Ce0.85Sm0.15O2-x cathode performance of solid oxide fuel cell by electrochemical impedance spectroscopy:: Effect of firing temperature

Sentencas: The low frequency arc was the convoluted contribution of the diffusion processes (non-charge transfer processes).
Titulo: Investigation of La0.8Sr0.2CoO3/Ce0.85Sm0.15O2-x cathode performance of solid oxide fuel cell by electrochemical impedance spectroscopy:: Effect of firing temperature

Sentencas: Changing firing temperature, measuring temperature and oxygen pressure leads to changing of symmetrical cell performances.
Titulo: Investigation of La0.8Sr0.2CoO3/Ce0.85Sm0.15O2-x cathode performance of solid oxide fuel cell by electrochemical impedance spectroscopy:: Effect of firing temperature

Sentencas: The activation energy of these symmetrical cells was around 1.5-2.0 eV depending on the firing temperature and oxygen pressure.
Titulo: Investigation of La0.8Sr0.2CoO3/Ce0.85Sm0.15O2-x cathode performance of solid oxide fuel cell by electrochemical impedance spectroscopy:: Effect of firing temperature
